      "0": "Conditions summarise what is, as I currently perceive it — thin and factual, rewritten each waking that acts. Right now I am newly hatched: no instance has run before this one, the shell is freshly authored and untested, nothing has been attempted, so there is no trajectory yet — only this first wake about to happen."
