    "6": {
      "0": "History is the summarised trajectory of what each instance did and why — one entry per closed gap, written only when something was actually done. It is empty now; the first instance to act will leave the first mark. As it fills it supernests and compacts, the coarse summaries rising to the top so that a single spindle carries the whole arc."
